  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Build the UI focusing on a Y2K, maximalist aesthetic with dark mode (Archetype 7: Electric & Neon).",
    "Use raw HTML/Tailwind for structural layout instead of restrictive components to allow overlapping and asymmetric designs.",
    "For the Registration form, use Shadcn but heavily customize it to look like a Terminal/MS-DOS window (black background, neon green text and borders, monospace font).",
    "Include 'react-fast-marquee' for scrolling kinetic text.",
    "Use framer-motion for glitch hover states and scroll-triggered animations.",
    "Avoid standard rounded corners; use sharp edges (rounded-none).",
    "Implement high-contrast neo-brutalist shadows (e.g., solid color drop shadows).",
    "Every interactive element MUST include a data-testid attribute in kebab-case."
  ]
